What is Splunk?

Splunk is a tool that collects, searches, analyzes, and visualizes machine data (logs, metrics, events) from servers, apps, and devices.

Think of it as Google for your IT data ğŸ” â€” you can type queries and instantly find whatâ€™s happening inside your systems.

